```
    elif isinstance(token, string_types):
        const = token[-2:].upper()
        if const not in Rule.weekdays:
            raise ValueError
        nth = token[:-2]
        if not nth:
            return Weekday(list(Rule.weekdays).index(const))  # defaulting index to None
        else:
            return Weekday(list(Rule.weekdays).index(const), int(nth))
```

